{"words":[{"word":"beast","count":7},{"word":"packages","count":3},{"word":"yeah","count":3},{"word":"dangerous","count":3},{"word":"thing","count":3},{"word":"talk","count":3},{"word":"jingle","count":3},{"word":"saved","count":2},{"word":"life","count":2},{"word":"remember","count":2},{"word":"sorry","count":2},{"word":"monster","count":2},{"word":"everyone's","count":2},{"word":"talking","count":2},{"word":"recently","count":2},{"word":"whatever","count":2},{"word":"man-eating","count":2},{"word":"said","count":2},{"word":"savages","count":2},{"word":"people","count":2},{"word":"paying","count":2},{"word":"attacking","count":2},{"word":"humans","count":2},{"word":"ferocious","count":2},{"word":"sir","count":2},{"word":"often","count":2},{"word":"phew","count":1},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"asking","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"run","count":1},{"word":"away","count":1},{"word":"reach","count":1},{"word":"recipients","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"promise","count":1},{"word":"deliver","count":1},{"word":"slogan","count":1},{"word":"lollo","count":1},{"word":"logistics","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"transferred","count":1},{"word":"station","count":1},{"word":"rarely","count":1},{"word":"anyone","count":1},{"word":"dropping","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"surely","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"hmm","count":1},{"word":"ring","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"bell","count":1},{"word":"m-maybe","count":1},{"word":"mistake","count":1},{"word":"twinkle","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"tusks","count":1},{"word":"sharp","count":1},{"word":"claws","count":1},{"word":"tear","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"shreds","count":1},{"word":"exile","count":1},{"word":"group","count":1},{"word":"called","count":1},{"word":"claim","count":1},{"word":"able","count":1},{"word":"sounds","count":1},{"word":"familiar","count":1},{"word":"tingle","count":1},{"word":"communicate","count":1},{"word":"rules","count":1},{"word":"f-follow","count":1},{"word":"cannot","count":1},{"word":"divulge","count":1},{"word":"details","count":1},{"word":"clients","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"found","count":1},{"word":"roaming","count":1},{"word":"campsite","count":1},{"word":"somewhere","count":1},{"word":"near","count":1},{"word":"broken","count":1},{"word":"tree","count":1},{"word":"mountainside","count":1},{"word":"working","count":1},{"word":"guard","count":1},{"word":"tower","count":1},{"word":"spot","count":1},{"word":"remind","count":1},{"word":"beyond","count":1},{"word":"wildest","count":1},{"word":"imagination","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"careful","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Phew... Thank you! You saved my life!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Thanks for asking. I'm fine. I could have run away, but then the packages wouldn't reach their recipients...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Of course! \"We Promise, We Deliver\"! That's our slogan at the Lollo Logistics!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"All packages must be transferred at this station, but we rarely see anyone dropping off their packages here. If someone did, I will surely remember them.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Sure! You just saved my life. I'll tell you everything I can remember!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Hmm, I'm sorry, but this doesn't ring any bell...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"...M-Maybe it was a mistake?","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"The \"Twinkle Beast\"? You mean that monster everyone's been talking about recently?","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Yeah, whatever. That dangerous, man-eating thing.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"It's said to have long tusks and sharp claws that can tear anything to shreds...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"And there's this Exile group, called \"The Savages,\" and they claim to be able to talk to that beast.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"So people have been paying them to talk the \"Jingle Beast\" out of attacking humans...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"\"The Savages\"... Yeah, sounds familiar...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Do you know the \"Tingle Beast\"? That monster everyone's been talking about recently.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Yeah, whatever. That dangerous, man-eating thing.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"It's said that they know how to communicate with that ferocious beast.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"So people have been paying them to talk the \"Jingle Beast\" out of attacking humans...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"That's all I know, sir.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"...Sorry, but we have our rules to f-follow... I cannot divulge details of our clients.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"But I heard the Jingle Beast is often found roaming in a campsite. It's somewhere near a broken tree, on that mountainside...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Those working on the guard tower can often spot it, too.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Sir, may I remind you...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"That thing is very dangerous... It's ferocious beyond your wildest imagination. Please be careful...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"And there may be more than one of them...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031}]}